pullRequest.title: KOGITO-778: [DMN Designer] Client-side marshalling tests
pullRequest.bodyText:
See https://issues.redhat.com/browse/KOGITO-778
This PR:

Removes the obsolete kie-wb-common-dmn-webapp-kogito-marshaller-tests module
Adds tests for the different JIRA reported during development of the client-side marshaller.
The remaining tests are listed in the JIRA description

I've reported two follow up JIRA to track issues encountered writing the tests:

https://issues.redhat.com/browse/DROOLS-5045
https://issues.redhat.com/browse/DROOLS-5046

nodes.bodyText: Please make this private static field of class, it is in each test.
Please ignore all new tests due to our issues running on jenkins
Please refactor/explain what the test does.
